Armor Enhancement, Lesser			KEY:Armor Enhancement (Lesser)	CLASSES:Artificer=1									SCHOOL:Transmutation	COMPS:S, M			CASTTIME:1 minute			RANGE:Touch		TARGETAREA:Armor or shield touched																																		DURATION:10 min./level					SAVEINFO:None (object)					SPELLRES:No (object)				SOURCELONG:Eberron Campaign Setting	SOURCESHORT:ECS		SOURCEPAGE:p.109	DESC:The armor or shield you touch temporarily gains a special ability commonly found on magic armor or shields. You can choose any special ability whose market price is equivalent to a +1 bonus or up to 5,000 gp, such as light fortification or shadow. The armor or shield does not need to have an existing enhancement bonus, nor does it gain one when you imbue it with this infusion. Material Component: An ointment made from rare spices and minerals, costing 10 gp.
