Repair Light Damage										CLASSES:Artificer,Sorcerer,Wizard=1							SCHOOL:Transmutation	COMPS:V, S			CASTTIME:1 standard action	RANGE:Touch		TARGETAREA:Construct touched																																			DURATION:Instantaneous					SAVEINFO:None						SPELLRES:No						SOURCELONG:Eberron Campaign Setting	SOURCESHORT:ECS		SOURCEPAGE:p.114	DESC:When laying your hands upon a construct that has at least 1 hit point remaining, or a living construct with -9 or more hit points, you transmute its structure to repair damage it has taken. The spell repairs 1d8 points of damage + 1 point per caster level (maximum +5).
